==== SYNOPSIS ==================================================================
Play 2048 in a terminal or with automation.

==== USAGE =====================================================================
Invoke 2048 with the syntax:

	2048 [<option>...]

Try '2048 --help' for more information.

==== DEPENDENCIES ==============================================================
2048 depends on curses.

==== INSTALLATION ==============================================================
To build 2048, type:

	make

To install 2048:

	make [DESTDIR=<path>] install

If not specified, DESTDIR is "/usr/local" by default.

